{
  "stem": "14463.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a large family, but there's two of them-- two of my uncles did not live in Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One lived in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He left Poland somewhere around 1928, '29.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my other uncle, Lizer-- which his name here in Australia, was Lester-- he lived in Sydney, Australia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was also married and had three children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was a merchant in leather.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When he married my mother, it was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In those days there were [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, there was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so when he married my mother, he came to live in Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from home, his parents, his father, and his family, were also in leather.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, if I may say so, can I speak something about my family in Bochnia?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now my grandfather Weinreich, Abraham Weinreich, started off an industry in Poland which exists still today.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were making what they call [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It comes from the city Zakopane, in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's a holiday resort.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jackets from lamb's leather, the lamb's wool, lamb's skins, and embroidered, for men, ladies, and also for children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so he came from this background.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Chrzanow, he started off a business, wholesale and retail of leather.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a successful business, but it was not a big business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a-- you see, my father had a completely different attitude to life, than say, the Schreiber family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For him, business was only a means to make a living.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And but he was a scholar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And therefore, his business, he did not-- he put effort into it, of course.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Otherwise he couldn't make a living.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was not the whole-- it wasn't-- the business was not his whole life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had different interests.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
